description: Performs a statistical comparison of one control vs muliptle treatment conditions
name: MTvC_app

factors.name: Measurement
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the values to use in the computation.

Example:
* log transform of S100
* log transformed and ComBat Corrected S100
* VSN transformed S100
* VSN transformed and ComBat Corrected S100

factors.name: Group
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the comparison groups.

Example:
* Test Condition
* Treatment off chip

factors.name: Variable
factors.description:
Select the peptide identifier.

Example:
* ID

factors.name: Observation
factors.description:
Select the factor(s) defining a single value per cell.

Example:
* Barcode and Row
* Barcode and Array
* Sample Name

factors.name: Pair
factors.description:
Select the factor which defines the pairing (if applicable). 

Example:
* Barcode
* Cell line
* Replicate
* Supergroup

filters.name: Control
filters.description:
Select the factor which defines the control.

Example:
* C-(DMSO, WT, Control)
